            <p>To Gaius Caelius Herma. Gaius Satrius Hermes and Accia Pollitta made (this)
               for (their) best friend, with the place given by leave of Calpurnia Praepusa.</p>
            <p>Intact inscription attested in <hi rend="italic">CIL</hi> VI, 13895.</p>
